<h3>How to share multiple links:</h3>
<ul>
<li>hold either "ctrl"(one at a time) or "shift"(get those in between) keys</li>
<li>click by your mouse left button on the needed tabs</li>
<li>click on extension icon</li>
<li>click on "share those tabs" button</li>
<li>copy the generated link, and share it</li>
</ul>
